def_cn: （建筑）破烂不堪的，摇摇欲坠的
def_en: A ramshackle building is badly made or in bad condition, and looks as if it is likely to fall down.

def_cn: （系统、联盟、收集物等）草率组合成的，拼凑的
def_en: A ramshackle system, union, or collection of things has been put together without much thought and is not likely to work very well.
